name: Zerenab
description:
I am a serious and mature woman, with good values-learned at home. Family is the first for me. I am respectful, honest, neat, organized and hardworking. I wish to find a good person to raise a pretty family. I like to keep my word and I expect the same from the others.
I need a sincere gentleman with good manners and intentions, respectful and detailing; somebody who likes to standout in work as much as in life. A man with good feelings who believes in honesty and will be my perfect man.
